{
  "page": "Malliard",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Alchemists%27_Guild\" title=\"Alchemists&#39; Guild\"><img alt=\"Pyromancer.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/6b/Pyromancer.svg/50px-Pyromancer.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/6b/Pyromancer.svg/75px-Pyromancer.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/6b/Pyromancer.svg/100px-Pyromancer.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Wisdom</span><br />Malliard</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Alchemists%27_Guild\" title=\"Alchemists&#39; Guild\"><img alt=\"Pyromancer.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/6b/Pyromancer.svg/50px-Pyromancer.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/6b/Pyromancer.svg/75px-Pyromancer.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/6b/Pyromancer.svg/100px-Pyromancer.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Wisdom\" title=\"Wisdom\">Wisdom</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Alchemists%27_Guild\" title=\"Alchemists&#39; Guild\">Alchemists' Guild</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Crownlands\" title=\"Crownlands\">Crownlands</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>Wisdom <b>Malliard</b> is a member of the <a href=\"/index.php/Alchemists%27_Guild\" title=\"Alchemists&#39; Guild\">Alchemists' Guild</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a>. He is in charge of keeping track and projecting production of the <a href=\"/index.php/Wildfire\" title=\"Wildfire\">wildfire</a> at the <a href=\"/index.php/Guildhall_of_the_Alchemists\" title=\"Guildhall of the Alchemists\">Guild Hall</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok20.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok20.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#A_Clash_of_Kings\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Behind_the_Scenes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Behind the Scenes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Malliard&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Clash_of_Kings\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Malliard&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Clash of Kings\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Hallyne\" title=\"Hallyne\">Hallyne</a> informs <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a> that Malliard expects the <a href=\"/index.php/Alchemists%27_Guild\" title=\"Alchemists&#39; Guild\">Alchemists' Guild</a> will be able to deliver ten thousand jars of <a href=\"/index.php/Wildfire\" title=\"Wildfire\">wildfire</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok20.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok20.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Behind_the_Scenes\">Behind the Scenes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Malliard&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Behind the Scenes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Malliard may be a reference by <a href=\"/index.php/George_R._R._Martin\" title=\"George R. R. Martin\">George R. R. Martin</a> to the chemist <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Louis_Camille_Maillard\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Louis Camille Maillard\">Louis Camille Maillard</a>, the namesake of the <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Maillard_reaction\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Maillard reaction\">Maillard reaction</a>. \n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Malliard&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok20.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok20.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok20.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_20\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 20\">Chapter 20</a>, Tyrion V.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404214631\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.065 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.256 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 474/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10426/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 5245/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 256/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 805/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.170/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.43 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  245.128      1 -total\n 97.11%  238.035      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 96.35%  236.173      1 Template:Infobox\n 10.75%   26.354     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  5.28%   12.945      4 Template:Infobox_label\n  2.15%    5.264      2 Template:Ref\n  1.25%    3.060      2 Template:Ref/core\n  0.64%    1.565      1 Template:References\n  0.37%    0.918      1 Template:Main_other\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:3639-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404214630 and revision id 315878\n -->\n",
